title: Out of Whack
description: We’ve been waiting for months to bring you this one: we can finally talk about the President’s Supreme Court Commission, which just finalized its report this week. We also briefly talk about the recent argument in Dobbs and try to predict what the Court might do.
author: pod@dividedargument.com (Will Baude & Dan Epps)
